# Pre-commit gate. Run lint-staged first (fast: formats staged files + a
# quick oxlint pass), then auto-fix any remaining oxfmt drift in the
# working tree so `pnpm lint` (which still has --check) always passes,
# then the heavier checks against the whole tree so untracked or
# cross-file regressions can't slip through.
pnpm lint-staged
pnpm format:fix
pnpm lint
pnpm typecheck
pnpm test